"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447231","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2016-01-28","<p>It is important to determine the facts of any incident. From current evidence we have seen, it does not appear that a Saudi airstrike hit the Iranian Embassy. We are continuing to work with all parties to de-escalate regional tensions.</p>","Runnymede and Weybridge","Mr Philip Hammond",,"2016-01-28T16:32:18.437Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447231/answer","Biography information for Mr Philip Hammond","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447231/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447231/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2016-01-25","Iran: Saudi Arabia","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, pursuant to the Answer of 21 January 2016 to Question 22858, on the basis of the evidence seen by the Government, what assessment he has made of who was responsible for the damage to the Iranian Embassy in Sana'a.","false","Biography information for Hilary Benn","Leeds Central","Hilary Benn","23905"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447232","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2016-02-02","<p>The Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, my right hon. Friend the Member for Runnymede and Weybridge (Mr Hammond) did not attend the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, in January 2016.</p>","East Devon","Mr Hugo Swire",,"2016-02-02T16:27:56.247Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447232/answer","Biography information for Sir Hugo Swire","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447232/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/447232/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2016-01-25","Foreign and Commonwealth Office: World Economic Forum","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, whether he visited the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, in January 2016, in his official capacity.","false","Biography information for Paul Flynn","Newport West","Paul Flynn","24019"
